HORACE to PINDAR might impute</br>His lofty tuneful Tongue:</br>And COWLEY'S MUSE had still been mute,</br>Had SPENSER'S never sung.
MAEVIUS makes D'URFEY'S Rhimes his own,</br>TOM'S Pegasus he tries:</br>And — was it not for tumbling down,</br>In Time might reach the Skies.
So School-Boys oft are seen to fail</br>In rearing of their Kite;</br>When heavy Papers load it's Tail,</br>And curb it's wonted Flight.</br>
